                <supplied reason="lost">Hanc pat</supplied>rona <supplied reason="lost">ti</supplied>bi statuit scholam Glen<supplied reason="lost">e merenti</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">erep</supplied>tum fato sustulit a<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>ra quies <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">floren</supplied>tem Parcae properastis toller<supplied reason="lost">e vitam</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">et no</supplied>n usuram parcere Ditis er<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">muta i</supplied>acet cinis et nomen tellure teg<supplied reason="lost">antur</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">secre</supplied>ti Manes ne sine fine satis
